@startuml
state Greeting as "System Greets User"
state CardInserted as "Card Inserted"
state PINCheck as "Checking PIN"
state IncorrectPIN as "Incorrect PIN Entered"
state KeepCard as "Keeping Card"
state ReturnCard as "Returning Card"
state OptionsMenu as "Displaying Options Menu"
state ProcessRequest as "Processing Request"

[*] --> Greeting : User Arrives
Greeting --> CardInserted : Card Inserted

CardInserted --> PINCheck : Checking PIN
PINCheck --> IncorrectPIN : Incorrect PIN
IncorrectPIN --> PINCheck : Try Again

PINCheck --> KeepCard : Invalid Card or Too Many Failed Attempts
KeepCard --> ReturnCard : User Cancels Operation
ReturnCard --> [*] : Card Returned

PINCheck --> OptionsMenu : Correct PIN Entered
OptionsMenu --> ProcessRequest : Request Selected
ProcessRequest --> [*] : Request Processed
@enduml
